<h1>Code Review Anxiety Workbook</h1>
<p>This interactive wizard walks you through the Code Review Anxiety Workbook (Lee &amp; Foster-Marks), a validated CBT intervention to help reduce anxiety around code reviews.</p>
<p>It takes about 10–15 minutes and will guide you through:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Rating your current anxiety level</li>
  <li>Optional physiological regulation (TIPP)</li>
  <li>Identifying and challenging biased thoughts</li>
  <li>Building a rational response</li>
  <li>Planning how to ask for or give a review</li>
</ul>

<%= form_with url: workbook_sessions_path, method: :post do |f| %>
  <%= f.submit "Get Started", class: "btn" %>
<% end %>
